sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Recruiter UI
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant WF as Temporal Workflow
    participant OBJ as Object Storage
    participant PARSE as Parsing Service
    participant AG as Agent Workers
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant VDB as Vector DB
    participant PDF as PDF Service

    UI->>API: Start candidate-job analysis
    API->>DB: Create workflow_run
    API->>WF: Start workflow
    WF->>OBJ: Load candidate files
    WF->>PARSE: Normalize documents
    PARSE->>DB: Save parsed text/chunks metadata
    PARSE->>VDB: Save embeddings
    WF->>AG: Run JD analysis agent
    WF->>AG: Run candidate extraction agent
    WF->>AG: Run interview insight agent
    WF->>AG: Run consistency/risk agent
    AG->>DB: Save structured facts and evidence
    WF->>DB: Load facts
    WF->>DB: Save deterministic scores
    WF->>AG: Draft structured report
    WF->>PDF: Render PDF
    PDF->>OBJ: Store PDF
    PDF->>DB: Save report metadata
    WF->>DB: Mark workflow complete
    API-->>UI: Report ready